      <div class="caption">Stress analysis of the Rooppur NPP cooling tower under dynamic loading — comparing Embedded Reinforcement and Simplified Column modelling approaches.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>Ongoing work</strong> includes CFRP-strengthened beam-column connections under monotonic and cyclic loading
    <em>(in submission, 2025)</em> and impact behaviour of pressurised uPVC pipes <em>(in preparation, 2025)</em>.
  </p>

